er-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/6839a3bd45bd3da1c7aa7634_cover-p-1080.png 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/6839a3bd45bd3da1c7aa7634_cover.png 1280w" class="blog-card-img"/></div><strong class="blog-card-title">LTV Calculator for SaaS</strong><p class="blog-card-text">Explore LTV calculation SaaS, why it matters, how to do it right, and how your results can drive smarter product, pricing, and growth decisions.</p></a></div><div role="listitem" class="blog-card w-dyn-item"><div class="blog-heading ml-lg pos-relative hover-disable"><div>article</div></div><a data-w-id="a1483318-f83b-f15b-e5b5-29f52e7cfdd4" href="9-key-saas-metrics-you-should-track-to-ensure-your-business-is-doing-great" class="blog-card-link w-inline-block"><div class="blog-card-img-wrap blog-card-img-wrap--xl"><img alt="image" loading="lazy" data-w-id="a1483318-f83b-f15b-e5b5-29f52e7cfdd6" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a8141f7655eb2dbc32383c_COVER_9%20Key%20SaaS%20Metrics%20You%20Should%20Track%20to%20Ensure%20Your%20Business%20Is%20Doing%20Great.png" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a8141f7655eb2dbc32383c_COVER_9%20Key%20SaaS%20Metrics%20You%20Should%20Track%20to%20Ensure%20Your%20Business%20Is%20Doing%20Great-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a8141f7655eb2dbc32383c_COVER_9%20Key%20SaaS%20Metrics%20You%20Should%20Track%20to%20Ensure%20Your%20Business%20Is%20Doing%20Great-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a8141f7655eb2dbc32383c_COVER_9%20Key%20SaaS%20Metrics%20You%20Should%20Track%20to%20Ensure%20Your%20Business%20Is%20Doing%20Great-p-1080.png 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a8141f7655eb2dbc32383c_COVER_9%20Key%20SaaS%20Metrics%20You%20Should%20Track%20to%20Ensure%20Your%20Business%20Is%20Doing%20Great.png 1280w"